name: brainbox-ibl
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "brainbox-ibl" %}
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}

 package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

 source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 8968ece4cba16a4b792cb0d06bf714007375b4c9c52c109fec52ceabc1a39d61

 build: 
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"
  noarch: python

 requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.0
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.0

 test:
  imports:
    - brainbox

 about:
  home: https://github.com/int-brain-lab/ibllib
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Library used to implement the International Brain Laboratory data pipeline

 extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jaib1
